_sText:
Hi, my name is SolDIEr of {Fortune} and this is my first map uploaded to Fpsbanana.

Inspired by some some particular maps, I tried to make a jailbreak map that combined both detail, comfortability and enjoyment. It is fair-sided, but requires a CT with a 'head on his shoulder'. 

I do believe this is unlike any other jailbreak map (that I have at least played). The layout is different, which makes it unique. Uniqueness is a good thing in my eyes. You'll notice that T's need to swim under CT spawn just to get to big cage. There a door opens which allows them to a hallway leading outside.

I do hope you enjoy this map. Feedback is greatly appreciated.


Enjoy!



-its soldier time
